            <title>[SOLR-3811] Search Form does not set defType when dismax/edismax boxes are checked</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3811</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Alexandre Rafalovitch noticed on the solr-user mailing list that if you click on the &quot;dismax&quot; (or &quot;edismax&quot;) checkbox in the Solr Admin UI, then you get an (unused) &quot;dismax=true&quot; param added to the URL instead of &quot;defType=dismax&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
